+-----------------------------------------------------------------------
| Running ${FULLPKGNAME} on OpenBSD
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------

To enable the compositor manager of metacity, use the following command:
    gconftool-2 -s '/apps/metacity/general/compositing_manager' \
      --type bool true

To disable it:
    gconftool-2 -s '/apps/metacity/general/compositing_manager' \
      --type bool false
